# AI Healthcare Assistant 🩺

This project is a simple AI-based web app that analyzes user symptoms and provides basic health suggestions.

## Features
- Symptom input
- AI-based response (rule-based for now)
- Simple UI

## Disclaimer
This is NOT a medical diagnosis tool.

## Run Locally

### Backend
cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py

### Frontend
Open index.html in browser
